data.description: CHIC AND COZY ELEGANCE!! This charming, one-level home in Greymoor Station in Trolley Run features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, upscale details, a private lot, and a convenient single garage. Inside, discover the elegance of hardwoods in the main living areas, complemented by crown molding, 9ft ceilings, wainscotting, and coffered ceilings in the dining area. The functional kitchen boasts granite counters, stainless steel appliances, an adorable breakfast area, and plenty of counter space for culinary adventures. The soaring vaulted ceiling in the living area creates a spacious feel, while natural light flows in through custom plantation shutters installed throughout the home. Enjoy the tranquility of the covered rear patio and the privacy of the fenced yard, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. This home only has one neighbor, as the adjacent lot is owned by the community and will not be developed. The HOA conveniently covers front and side lawn maintenance, leaving you more time to enjoy the rocking chair front porch. Don't miss the chance to make this your Home Sweet Home! Conveniently located near USC Aiken, Aiken Regional Hospital, the Family Y, and is just a few mins to Downtown Aiken, Bridgestone, and Exit 11 at I-20.
